{
  "stem": "20088.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But he said if God forbid one of us get caught, at least we-- the other part has a chance to get through.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we divide the chances.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the second thing was it very difficult to find a hiding place for a family of four.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't think in Amsterdam it would have been possible.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Perhaps if you would have gone to the country to a farm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But in town, I don't think that was possible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The houses weren't so big to accommodate so many people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He got all those from a man from the underground movement.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He must have been in touch with-- with him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Brooksma.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a teacher.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father had a-- a Christian friend, a-- a lady.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he had put-- because we rented this flat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But at the time already he put the-- the rent of this flat not in our name, but in this lady's name.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But this-- I-- I knew the name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it-- I've forgotten it now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This lady-- as soon as my father said we were going to move out, she was only lived in room.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She said, you move into this flat, and it's your flat anyway.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she moved into this flat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I noticed that he suffered a lot that-- as I say, the family was for him everything because he had lost-- lost his mother at a very early age.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And his father too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so he had a stepmother at first, a bad stepmother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he really wanted to give his family everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he felt terrible that he was sort of powerless to protect us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He tried his best, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But as it turned out, it wasn't really enough.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
